{"tid":2516863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一位母親投訴超市化妝品膚色選項有限，構成「種族歧視」","createTime":"2021-05-05T02:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:44:05.000Z","uid":124021,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"eccd3d9ded31d18e3af2d2325c56cef36c9a82f1","tid":2516863,"uid":124021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"一位婦女投訴兩大澳洲超市巨頭「種族歧視」？逾2000人支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報道，這一位母親投訴澳洲兩大連鎖超市，指貨架上的化妝品膚色選項有限，讓有色人種難以選擇，構成「種族歧視」。<br />\n<br />\n威林克（Rebecca Willink）在線上聯署的請願書上<span class=\"pink\">，指 Coles 及 Woolworths 兩間大型連鎖超市無論在店內還是線上的化妝品都缺乏深色膚色的選項，是不公平的。</span><br />\n<br />\n她表示，有色人種目前無法從超市中選擇正確色調的粉底液或其他化妝品，因為這些產品並不在貨架上。因此，<span class=\"orange\">有較深膚色的人最終要付出更高昂的費用前往其他地方購買適合他們的粉底</span>，因為她們無法從超市取得。<br />\n<br />\n她認為有限的顏色選擇，發放一個清晰的訊息就是他們不被重視，讓她感覺不如其他澳洲人般屬於這裡。<br />\n<br />\n她說，這是歧視的一種，必須要立即解決。<br />\n<br />\n她的請願書目前已收集了 2,000 多個簽名，她的目標為 2,500。"},{"pid":"3feff60083067bf0124e87bd58894ade126a545f","tid":2516863,"uid":266428,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母係咪遲早話白紙太白歧視你,要全世界用環保紙"},{"pid":"a2d1e6629669c6b714bba4825ff24d6308e8ac30","tid":2516863,"uid":20018,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"買碳粉咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a81c723866d202805775f1b491043698ac3d12","tid":2516863,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"要黑色曬黑就得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7db70cff2433cde024ff4607a9987af4dc4653","tid":2516863,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:46:13.000Z","msg":"唔滿意咪咪撚化囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a88f7857394dcf4c95d784ca52d59210327820","tid":2516863,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6fc6192b301571bf89cfe527440e4c49ede132","tid":2516863,"uid":292987,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"其實真係諗過會有呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜黑色foundation好失禮你咩？係都要跟自己膚色買ivory，仲話唔係racist？"},{"pid":"4f8988b9c4b6e781ef44de30992d07583e1fa994","tid":2516863,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"阿嬌走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a1ab3df88daf52d87507e13147d04da9f81c02","tid":2516863,"uid":93784,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"唔係人地歧視你 <br />\n係你自己歧視自己膚色姐<br />\n乜野都標籤做種族歧視 搏人同情<br />\n件事同種族歧視無關係<br />\n人地產品唔適合你 唔等如 歧視你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07211057c1655ea09920fadf2d58679486b69a9b","tid":2516863,"uid":292987,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:51:55.000Z","msg":"之前睇過個YouTube廣告 sell個牌子粉底液調色好準確 作為對比有個白人女用其他牌子一試用明顯係偏黃黑，佢皺曬眉頭話no no no⋯⋯當時心諗點解仲未批鬥到呢條廣告片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068743768ad143859c71b43c6f5c675178b78a84","tid":2516863,"uid":37631,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"諗起呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaxoV1jCuPG3VuGt11FHJGVy3CUDhWWczh4XvX7ogVQFR?filename=MWhFF0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWhFF0t.jpg&h=5228e35e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2f3c125014d9401244ed99b33de1c3fd4e85c9","tid":2516863,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"可樂夠歧視白人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p